dismissalText.commentary: Virender Sehwag run out (Watson) 37 (40b 4x4 1x6 89m) SR: 92.5

dismissalComment.html: RUN OUT! off the pad to the leg side, they take off for a dangerous single, Watson sprints across, the pick up is perfect and diving forward he flicks the ball at the stumps, Sehwag is out by a long way - 6 down 4 more to get

milestones.description: Hussey and Shane Watson's 145-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 136 between Hussey and Clarke
Flintoff and Sehwag's 60-run partnership is ICC's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 7 between Pietersen and Sangakkara
Shaun Pollock and Rahul Dravid's 20-run partnership is ICC's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 15 between Rahul Dravid and Pietersen
Brian Lara has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for ICC, going past Glenn McGrath's 1
Brian Lara has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for ICC, going past Vettori
Brian Lara has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for ICC, going past Vettori's 2
Shaun Pollock has conceded the most runs in an innings (67) in ODIs for ICC, going past Flintoff's record of 66
